<b>a spear and caught the other one by the</b>

85
00:03:18,433 --> 00:03:20,433
<b>throat, wrung its neck and</b>

86
00:03:20,433 --> 00:03:22,566
<b>choked it. If that sounds more</b>

87
00:03:22,566 --> 00:03:25,666
<b>like a fairy tale than history, hold that</b>

88
00:03:25,666 --> 00:03:27,433
<b>thought. They marry and</b>

