98
00:03:49,633 --> 00:03:51,766
<b>instead of reconciling,</b>

99
00:03:51,766 --> 00:03:54,933
<b>Lagertha goes home and murders her second</b>

100
00:03:54,933 --> 00:03:57,333
<b>husband with a spear tip</b>

