108
00:04:14,333 --> 00:04:17,333
<b>Saxo was a 12th century Christian cleric</b>

109
00:04:17,333 --> 00:04:19,933
<b>writing propaganda. His goal</b>

110
00:04:19,933 --> 00:04:21,866
<b>was to make pre-Christian</b>

