114
00:04:29,066 --> 00:04:31,533
<b>Christian audience, a woman</b>

115
00:04:31,533 --> 00:04:34,266
<b>who fights is unnatural, savage.</b>

116
00:04:34,266 --> 00:04:36,533
<b>Look at his phrasing again.</b>

117
00:04:36,533 --> 00:04:39,166
<b>"Though a maiden, had the courage of a</b>

118
00:04:39,166 --> 00:04:41,533
