00:07:53,466 --> 00:07:56,333
<b>two shields, 25 arrows, horses,</b>

192
00:07:56,333 --> 00:07:59,033
<b>and a full set of gaming pieces. If this</b>

193
00:07:59,033 --> 00:08:02,433
<b>burial was just symbolic of family status,</b>

194
00:08:02,433 --> 00:08:05,400
<b>they committed hard to the bit. So what's</b>

195
00:08:05,400 --> 00:08:08,333
<b>the actual truth about Lagertha? The TV show?</b>

196
00:08:08,333 --> 00:08:12,366
<b>About 80% fiction. It borrowed Lagertha's</b>

197
00:08:12,366 --> 00:08:14,233
