206
00:08:35,300 --> 00:08:37,666
<b>through religious bias. But</b>

207
00:08:37,666 --> 00:08:40,600
<b>the archaeology? That's real. The Birka</b>

208
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:42,766
<b>grave proves at least one</b>

