<b>remarkable because she was unusual. So</b>

221
00:09:14,533 --> 00:09:17,633
<b>here's the uncomfortable reality.</b>

222
00:09:17,633 --> 00:09:20,533
<b>Lagertha was probably just a</b>

223
00:09:20,533 --> 00:09:23,033
<b>story medieval Christians</b>

224
00:09:23,033 --> 00:09:25,366
<b>told about pagan ancestors,</b>

225
00:09:25,366 --> 00:09:28,366
<b>filtered through biases, mixed with</b>

226
00:09:28,366 --> 00:09:31,500
<b>mythology, shaped by propaganda. But</b>

227
00:09:31,500 --> 00:09:33,433
<b>here's what matters.</b>

228
00:09:33,433 --> 00:09:36,766
